# LoCoMo reproducibility artifacts are sha256-pinned in
# benchmarks/locomo/artifacts/MANIFEST.json and verified by rescore.mjs.
# Disable end-of-line conversion so the bytes — and therefore the hashes —
# are byte-identical on every platform. Without this, a Windows checkout with
# core.autocrlf=true would smudge LF->CRLF in the working tree and break the
# integrity check on a fresh clone.
benchmarks/locomo/artifacts/*.jsonl               -text
benchmarks/locomo/artifacts/dataset-MANIFEST.json -text
benchmarks/locomo/artifacts/sample-MANIFEST.json  -text
